?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0000060NN" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'I Want You-Marvin Gaye']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fi-want-you%252Fid17016259%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'I Want You-Marvin Gaye']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2011/07/nowhere.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/nowhere.jpg" alt="Nowhere / Ride" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2011/07/nowhere.php">Nowhere<br />Ride</a></h4><p>轟音ギターの壁の後ろに、繊細と虚無を抱えて逃げる、みたいな若者たち。美しい旋律とギターアンサンブルが光ります。フィードバック音に身を預ければ"どこでもない"所へトリップ。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005NNS5/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005NNS5" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Nowhere-Ride']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fnowhere%252Fid352900411%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Nowhere-Ride']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2011/07/causers-of-this.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/causersofthis.jpg" alt="CAUSERS OF THIS / Toro y Moi" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2011/07/causers-of-this.php">CAUSERS OF THIS<br />Toro y Moi</a></h4><p>佳曲の数々と甘い歌声にとろけて気持ちは彼方へ飛んでいきます。引いてるのにポジティブ。ポップと先鋭と音響の愉悦。うまくかわしていくことの大切さと強靭さ。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002WMGF3K/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002WMGF3K" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'CAUSERS OF THIS-Toro y Moi']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fcausers-of-this%252Fid349064504%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'CAUSERS OF THIS-Toro y Moi']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

